{"tid":490850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[HK No IT]警破網上拍賣騙案拉IT男","createTime":"2017-12-06T03:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T07:13:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"925254d451e697461c27faa9ac81ab36b5c17b3c","tid":490850,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T03:48:19.000Z","msg":"沙田刑事調查隊督察王頌然指，被捕男子31歲姓方，據悉，<span style=\"color: red;\">從事資訊科技工作</span>，警方根據他登記的銀行戶口資料，將其拘捕。受害人至少涉及24人，年齡由17歲至50餘歲，涉款約7萬港元。警方呼籲網上交易要小心，如有懷疑應該即時停止及報案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/bkn-20171206085002723-1206_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171206%2Fbkn-20171206085002723-1206_00822_001.html&d=6ll5re8GSRzNTKtVJkaB4m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=423e4094\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/bkn-20171206085002723-1206_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"111691dc2cd781e6f93dd6135b87b56d630360a1","tid":490850,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T03:48:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">從事資訊科技工作<br />\n從事資訊科技工作<br />\n從事資訊科技工作<br />\n從事資訊科技工作</span>"},{"pid":"71689d9473a6eb5a5160190d97de1786709c499a","tid":490850,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T03:49:32.000Z","msg":"IT=罪惡"},{"pid":"a1b182e03c26e6d4597bf5a2033400b6ae286ade","tid":490850,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T03:49:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>IT=罪惡</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203753275a342de8a723971c7ec2d8a129833605","tid":490850,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T03:50:50.000Z","msg":"IT雖受到社會各階層的歡迎，但以IT為生的職業低層員工卻屬於「賤民」，地位在基層市民之下。雖然有些當紅的IT人，能夠擠身豪們，成為達官貴人的座上客，然而在世人的眼中，他們的人格仍然是低下的，因為IT是供人娛樂的「玩意兒」，IT人就是為人取樂的。<br />\n<br />\n看不起IT人並不僅僅是官員，市民也同樣視IT為最下賤的職業。普通人家如有人去做「IT」，都會被認為是有辱家人，是不肖子孫。凡做「IT」的人要被開除族籍，名字不能上族譜，死後不能葬入宗族墳地。因此，很多人從IT之後，隱姓埋名，幾十年不與家人來往，以免玷辱祖宗。"},{"pid":"761d5f5c6ec1c09b6d837b4c2147684700b27f6a","tid":490850,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T03:51:22.000Z","msg":"低端人口"},{"pid":"37849750eb44aedded67205189921581c910212e","tid":490850,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T03:51:52.000Z","msg":"老貓有冇IT狗犯罪紀錄"},{"pid":"2c0f32c23d720dc055774e8dea3aca41f622a6f8","tid":490850,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"林祖舜分享了 Live &amp; Found 的影片。<br />\n<br />\n聴日就DSE放榜啦，想當年我都好緊張、同朋友去咗尖東坐通宵。其實我個會考個成績好一般，最後都入唔到最想入o個科，之後入咗去讀IT（我當時連Bill Gates都唔識）、先發覺我對IT都好有興趣，所以想同大家講人生有好多條路可以行、就算考得唔好都唔係世界未日、行唔到Plan A咪行Plan B o攞、千其唔好灰心、仲有排行呀、加油！"},{"pid":"fc5f8fb60b64e54378ca2de59a7510b895df67c4","tid":490850,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:06:59.000Z","msg":"it撚表示 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e90464d79b60c2d9483febfe23de213bf77265","tid":490850,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老貓有冇IT狗犯罪紀錄</blockquote><br />\n厚過電話簿"},{"pid":"bb3d07c191e922af3d5717841cf34d3bcbcbd7a4","tid":490850,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老貓有冇IT狗犯罪紀錄</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早期：BT 老翻<br />\n<br />\n跟住有一輪勁多IT狗玩偷拍，拉曬<br />\n<br />\n又扮放LAN線，捐枱底摸OL腳，又拉一堆<br />\n<br />\n總結：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IT是原罪</span>"},{"pid":"90539c143a3716f873564ed1f9a0af1158b168cd","tid":490850,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:22:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老貓有冇IT狗犯罪紀錄</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早期：BT 老翻<br />\n<br />\n跟住有一輪勁多IT狗玩偷拍，拉曬<br />\n<br />\n又扮放LAN線，捐枱底摸OL腳，又拉一堆<br />\n<br />\n總結：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IT是原罪</span></bl